learning_outcomes.en:
The student: 
- applied various activities and methods depending on the specificity of the youth work field, its purpose, the target group, the place of youth work and situations; 
- explains the content of youth work and to introduce opportunities in the youth field;
- designs work with young people in a safe environment, following the safety requirements set by  the legislation; - responds appropriately in emergency situations;
- supports other youth workers;
- analyses oneself and own practice experience using different methods; 
- sets goals for self-development; 
- assesses new techniques and methods.
